Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Software Developer* with *AspenTech*. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack web applications, distributed systems, and AI-driven automation, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

