I have always been passionate about *optimizing assets to run faster, longer, safer, and greener* and envision myself contributing my talent to the furthering of *autonomous, sustainable industrial operations*. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

